{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "07", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "04", "M": "23", "S": "03"}}, "news": [{"title": "Odisha registered 7,037 flats in last three years: Revenue minister", "para": "Odisha registered 7,037 flats in three years, boosting buyer ownership and land records. While 2024 saw a surge with 4,712 registrations, 2025 experienced a sharp decline to 593. Stricter scrutiny, enforcement of apartment laws, and action against erring officials contributed to the dip, with Khurda leading registrations.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/odishas-revenue-minister-reports-7037-flats-registered-over-three-years/130074553?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-47686/130074553.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Indore: 100 commercial buildings get final 48-hour ultimatum over fire safety", "para": "Indore authorities are intensifying a crackdown on fire safety violations, targeting around 100 commercial buildings. Building owners have until April 8 to install mandatory fire safety equipment or face immediate sealing and punitive action. This stern warning follows a survey revealing significant gaps in fire safety measures across the city.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/final-ultimatum-for-100-indore-commercial-buildings-fire-safety-compliance-required/130074313?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-58566/130074313.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Lucknow development body's three luxury housing projects to take off soon", "para": "Construction of three luxury housing projects by the Lucknow Development Authority is set to begin soon. Work orders are expected within a month. These projects will offer around 1,060 flats with prices ranging from Rs 70 lakh to Rs 2.80 crore. Registration is open for some schemes, with others nearing completion of allotment.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/ldas-luxury-housing-projects-in-lucknow-set-to-launch-soon/130074227?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-26838/130074227.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}